title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick show, DP sounds off on the people that allowed Tua Tagovailoa to play yesterday. Former NFL Safety Rodney Harrison discusses playing with a concussion. FOX College Football Analyst Matt Leinart relays a message for a coworker about a bone they have to pick with DP.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
